lead_paragraph: Genoa blew away Serie A leaders Juventus on Sunday, getting three goals in an astonishing first half-hour on the way to a pulsating 3-1 win.

headline.print_headline: Serie A Leaders Juventus Blown Away by Genoa in Half an Hour
